title: ADENGL Elevated Dog Bowls for Large Dogs with Sprill Proof Mat, Raised Dog Bowl Stand with Dog Food & Water Bowls, 39.5cm Tall Dog Feeder for Extra Large Breed-2000ml-Dog Bowls, Mat-50x80cm
features: 【SUITABLE FOR LARGE DOGS & EXTRA LARGE BREED】- ADENGL elevated dog bowls are designed for large and giant dogs, the bowl stand is approximately 39.5cm/15.5 inches high from bottom to top, perfectly suited for large breed, 67oz of large-capacity dog bowls to meet the dog's daily dietary needs, reducing the hassle of frequent filling!

【REDUCES STRESS ON JOINTS】- Compared with traditional dog food bowls, ADENGL dog bowl elevated provides a healthier way for dogs to eat, and the comfortable height can help them enjoy their food with less pressure on their neck and spine, which will effectively prevent joint diseases. Perfect for large dogs with limited mobility or joint problems!

【NO MORE MESSY FLOORS】- The ADENGL dog bowl stand comes with a splash-proof mat that can be placed underneath the bowl rack, spilled food and water can be well collected by the mat to keep the feeding area dry and tidy. Perfect for messy eaters.

【STABLE & DURABLE】- Our raised dog bowl is made of high quality rust-resistant metal material and powder coated steel, which is stronger and more durable than plastic food bowl stand. The bottom of the bowl rack is fitted with non-slip feet to hold the dog food bowls firmly in place and prevent your dog from tipping over while eating
【EASY TO ASSEMBLE】- Taking only 2 minute to assemble, the dog bowl set includes 2 food-grade stainless steel dog bowls (2000ML), a splash proof mat (50x80 inches), and other assembly accessories
